So I guess that `imageNamePrefix` is a redundancy here.
In a second thought what I should have done in #399 is to remove the following part

```
if len(img.Names) > 0 {
    image = img.Names[0]
}
```

Because If `img != nil` it means the image name given by the user exists and thus there is no need to assign a value to `image`.

